com.soa.message

Interface TransactedExchange


  • public interface TransactedExchange
    Holds information about a message exchange in a transaction. A transaction may consist of multiple exchanges executed in sequence. Each exchange may also spawn multiple exchanges of it's own, creating a hierarchy of exchanges in one transaction.

      • getPropertyNames

        java.util.Set getPropertyNames()
        Returns the names of the properties associated with the exchange. Changes made to the Set are reflected in the exchange, so if a name is removed from the Set, the property is removed from the exchange. Names cannot be added however.
        Returns:
        Set of String property names.
